#. type: Plain text
#: doc/tin.5:1156
msgid ""
"This file provides short descriptions of each mailgroup. (requires B<\\"
"%tin>(1)  to be built with mh-mail-handling support). Each line consist of "
"two tab-separated fields \"I<mailgroupname> I<one-line description>\"."
